@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "_MyLayout";
}

<style>
    body {
        background-image: url('/mine.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position: center 20%;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        background-blend-mode: overlay;
    }

    h1, h2, p ,li{
        background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.6); /* Semi-transparent gray */
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
</style>

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<h2>🛠️ Technologies Used</h2>
<p>
    This system utilizes the following technologies to ensure efficiency and security:
    <ul>
        <li>📌<b>ASP.NET Core</b> – Robust backend framework for scalable applications.</li>
        <li>📌<b>Entity Framework Core</b> – Efficient ORM for managing database interactions.</li>
        <li>📌<b>SQL Server</b> – Secure database management for healthcare data.</li>
        <li>📌<b>ASP.NET Core Identity</b> – User authentication and access control.</li>
        <li>📌<b>RESTful APIs</b> – Seamless integration with external systems.</li>
        <li>📌<b>Bootstrap & CSS</b> – Enhanced user interface and styling.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<h2>💡 System Capabilities</h2>
<p>
    The hospital management system provides the following key functionalities:
    <ul>
        <li>📌 <b>Secure Patient Record Management</b> – Ensures all medical data is safely stored.</li>
        <li>📌 <b>Doctor Appointment Scheduling</b> – Allows efficient booking and tracking of appointments.</li>
        <li>📌 <b>Advanced Data Encryption</b> – Protects sensitive patient information.</li>
        <li>📌 <b>Hospital Resource Management</b> – Streamlines staff and equipment allocation.</li>
        <li>📌 <b>Role-Based Access Control</b> – Ensures authorized access to data via ASP.NET Core Identity.</li>
        <li>📌 <b>Detailed Reports & Analytics</b> – Generates medical insights to support decision-making.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<h2>🔒 Data Protection & Security</h2>
<p>
    - All patient records are stored securely and **never shared with third parties** without explicit consent.
    - We implement **advanced encryption** and strict authentication mechanisms.
    - User access is controlled via **ASP.NET Core Identity**, ensuring proper authorization.
</p>

<h2>📜 Information Usage</h2>
<p>
    - Patient and hospital data is used **only for healthcare management purposes**.
    - The system collects necessary data to improve medical care and streamline operations.
    - Users have the right to request **modifications or deletions** of their stored data upon approval.
</p>

<h2>✅ Compliance & Updates</h2>
<p>
    - The system complies with **standard healthcare regulations** to protect data.
    - Regular **security updates and audits** ensure system integrity.
    - Any modifications to this policy will be communicated transparently.
</p>

<p>Thank you for trusting **Ahmed's Hospital Management System**. Your privacy and data security are our priority.</p>